title: Neil Young - Done It 100 Times (EP)2018
description:
Neil Young - Done It 100 Times (EP)2018

This is a Lil EP I grabbed from 100 Times or More - 4-CD Live compilaton.
Here is part of what is said about the Idea behind the creation of it... 

The compilation is inspired by the song 4 strong winds (I've been trough that a hundred times or more) and the compilation at the other side of the spectrum; 5 times or less. I Figured that a compilation like this might be interesting, since all the songs have been played so many times that there's a SBD avaliable. Also, there are bound to be some interesting versions around due to the many style changes. It sometimes is surprising what songs DO show up and what songs DON'T.

Thats enough. Listen to this and know that the 4 CD version is just as good. Just much bigger try the sampler and voice your yay or nay LOL

Tracklist

01 Sedan Delivery.mp3
02 Cowgirl In The Sand.mp3
03 Cortez The Killer.mp3
04 Down By The River.mp3

I took these at almost random from all 4 Disks
If enough peeps want I wlll share the whole thing
emjoy
